Codebase for yield modeling in lithography simulation.

Besides regular NumPy, SciPy, etc. modules, need the following modules:
cv2
pytest





Run the tests with the following command:
"pytest tests/test_basics.py" (or similar for different test files).

Run a single test with the following command (or similar):
pytest tests/test_dd_single_patterning.py::test_dd_1D_LS

You can turn on the plotting functions with "--plot".
You can turn on printing to terminal with "-s --print".

You can run all tests with the following command:
"pytest"
